kutengeneza Laravel Scheduled Tasks kwenye window

Tengeneza scheduled task

Fungua Task scheduler
Chagua Create Task...
Ipe task yako jina (name) na maelezo(description)
Kufanya task iwe inafanya kazi haijalishi mtu amelogin au la. Chagua the user is logged on or not na pia check  Hidden checkbox.

## Triggers
Tengeneza new trigger.
Panga trigger ifanye kazi kila siku (Daily)na pia iwe inatokea kila baada ya siku moja (1 day). 
panga iwe inarudia kila baada ya 1 Minutes. Kwa bahati mbaya uwezi kuchagua 1 minutes basi usiwe na shaka we chakua 5 minutes kisha badilisha  weka 1 minutes
Panga kwa kipindi cha (duration of) to indefinitely
Hakikisha kwamba umecheck Enabled

## Actions
Tengeneza new action.
Anzisha php kwa kuingiza php binary location, kama C:\php\php.exe
Weka Add argument field hivi C:\{project-dir}\artisan schedule:run (replace {project-dir} with appropriate path).

Settings
Check task zote zianze pale unapotaka (run on demand).
Check task ziwe zinaanza tena mara tu zinaposhidwa kufanya kazi (scheduled start is missed)

Jumuisho
Hakikisha kama task ina fanya kazi, tafuta task kwenye Task Sheduler Library
Angalia task Status. inaweza ikawa Ready au Running
Angalia Next Run Time na Last Run Time propersties

